{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020-01-14-observable-creation/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"박준우 블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d3c11149-2d79-56b4-9260-8c588d7cce52","excerpt":"RxJS를 조금씩 공부하고 있습니다. 옵저버블의 개념에 대해서는 옵저버블{:target=”_blank”} 에 아주 거칠고 투박하고 나만 알아먹게 첫느낌 정도로만 정리해두었습니다. 더 정제된 글로 다듬어야겠네요.. 이 글에서는 RxJS…","html":"<p>RxJS를 조금씩 공부하고 있습니다.</p>\n<p>옵저버블의 개념에 대해서는 <a href=\"https://junwoo45til.netlify.com/#/RxJS/observable\">옵저버블</a>{:target=”_blank”} 에 아주 거칠고 투박하고 나만 알아먹게 첫느낌 정도로만 정리해두었습니다.</p>\n<p>더 정제된 글로 다듬어야겠네요..</p>\n<p>이 글에서는 RxJS의 수많은 오퍼레이터 중에서도 생성에 관련된 오퍼레이터들을 몇 개 정리해보았습니다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2>create</h2>\n<p>: 주어진 subscription 함수를 옵저버블로 만듭니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 561px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/127aa42b04feac1ada1c642ff323d8c6/410f3/observable_creation10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60.75949367088608%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"create1\"\n        title=\"create1\"\n        src=\"/static/127aa42b04feac1ada1c642ff323d8c6/410f3/observable_creation10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/127aa42b04feac1ada1c642ff323d8c6/c26ae/observable_creation10.png 158w,\n/static/127aa42b04feac1ada1c642ff323d8c6/6bdcf/observable_creation10.png 315w,\n/static/127aa42b04feac1ada1c642ff323d8c6/410f3/observable_creation10.png 561w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 561px) 100vw, 561px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 error를 만나면, 다음 next는 옵저버에게 전달되지않고 종료된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e2d1a703a7e4c27db253df435e3d191f/9bb7a/observable_creation11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.835443037974684%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"create2\"\n        title=\"create2\"\n        src=\"/static/e2d1a703a7e4c27db253df435e3d191f/f058b/observable_creation11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e2d1a703a7e4c27db253df435e3d191f/c26ae/observable_creation11.png 158w,\n/static/e2d1a703a7e4c27db253df435e3d191f/6bdcf/observable_creation11.png 315w,\n/static/e2d1a703a7e4c27db253df435e3d191f/f058b/observable_creation11.png 630w,\n/static/e2d1a703a7e4c27db253df435e3d191f/9bb7a/observable_creation11.png 676w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>complete에게는 value값을 넘길 수 없구나..</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/25ff0769b7978cf76c1c9c3e6c87cbc0/374ac/observable_creation12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.43037974683544%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"create3\"\n        title=\"create3\"\n        src=\"/static/25ff0769b7978cf76c1c9c3e6c87cbc0/f058b/observable_creation12.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/25ff0769b7978cf76c1c9c3e6c87cbc0/c26ae/observable_creation12.png 158w,\n/static/25ff0769b7978cf76c1c9c3e6c87cbc0/6bdcf/observable_creation12.png 315w,\n/static/25ff0769b7978cf76c1c9c3e6c87cbc0/f058b/observable_creation12.png 630w,\n/static/25ff0769b7978cf76c1c9c3e6c87cbc0/374ac/observable_creation12.png 634w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h2>from</h2>\n<p>: 배열이나 프로미스, 또는 이터러블을 옵저버블로 바꿔준다.</p>\n<h4>1. Observable from array</h4>\n<p>배열의 요소 하나하나가 next메소드를 통해 옵저버에게 전달된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/089e7fa4c992c6d3112cd2584620ce7c/f058b/observable_creation5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.202531645569614%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"from1\"\n        title=\"from1\"\n        src=\"/static/089e7fa4c992c6d3112cd2584620ce7c/f058b/observable_creation5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/089e7fa4c992c6d3112cd2584620ce7c/c26ae/observable_creation5.png 158w,\n/static/089e7fa4c992c6d3112cd2584620ce7c/6bdcf/observable_creation5.png 315w,\n/static/089e7fa4c992c6d3112cd2584620ce7c/f058b/observable_creation5.png 630w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>완료가 되면 옵저버에게는 complete notification이 전달 되고, 실행된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 617px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9ebdb74e710976fa01263db6d389c40a/bc962/observable_creation8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.278481012658226%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"from1-1\"\n        title=\"from1-1\"\n        src=\"/static/9ebdb74e710976fa01263db6d389c40a/bc962/observable_creation8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9ebdb74e710976fa01263db6d389c40a/c26ae/observable_creation8.png 158w,\n/static/9ebdb74e710976fa01263db6d389c40a/6bdcf/observable_creation8.png 315w,\n/static/9ebdb74e710976fa01263db6d389c40a/bc962/observable_creation8.png 617w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 617px) 100vw, 617px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>2. Observable from promise</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dafee3b9e7a481f2b806a3a26282825f/8bd7c/observable_creation6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.316455696202528%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"from2\"\n        title=\"from2\"\n        src=\"/static/dafee3b9e7a481f2b806a3a26282825f/f058b/observable_creation6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dafee3b9e7a481f2b806a3a26282825f/c26ae/observable_creation6.png 158w,\n/static/dafee3b9e7a481f2b806a3a26282825f/6bdcf/observable_creation6.png 315w,\n/static/dafee3b9e7a481f2b806a3a26282825f/f058b/observable_creation6.png 630w,\n/static/dafee3b9e7a481f2b806a3a26282825f/8bd7c/observable_creation6.png 845w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4>3. Observable from collection</h4>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/93548b408511769943a0945119dd9848/8ce52/observable_creation7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.67088607594937%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"from3\"\n        title=\"from3\"\n        src=\"/static/93548b408511769943a0945119dd9848/f058b/observable_creation7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/93548b408511769943a0945119dd9848/c26ae/observable_creation7.png 158w,\n/static/93548b408511769943a0945119dd9848/6bdcf/observable_creation7.png 315w,\n/static/93548b408511769943a0945119dd9848/f058b/observable_creation7.png 630w,\n/static/93548b408511769943a0945119dd9848/8ce52/observable_creation7.png 681w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h2>fromEvent</h2>\n<p>:DOM 이벤트를 옵저버블로 바꿔줍니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/08f8323af25f7d3fc5e0650d71222fe7/6da96/observable_creation9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.37974683544304%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"fromEvent\"\n        title=\"fromEvent\"\n        src=\"/static/08f8323af25f7d3fc5e0650d71222fe7/f058b/observable_creation9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/08f8323af25f7d3fc5e0650d71222fe7/c26ae/observable_creation9.png 158w,\n/static/08f8323af25f7d3fc5e0650d71222fe7/6bdcf/observable_creation9.png 315w,\n/static/08f8323af25f7d3fc5e0650d71222fe7/f058b/observable_creation9.png 630w,\n/static/08f8323af25f7d3fc5e0650d71222fe7/6da96/observable_creation9.png 922w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h2>interval</h2>\n<p>:정해진 시간 간격으로 숫자를 생성해낸다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63f2320b2a130045306942cbf2545e13/b2cef/observable_creation3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.075949367088604%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAHCAIAAACHqfpvAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAdklEQVQY06XNyw7CMAxE0fz/V7KpCCltM7EzDhE0PITYQEsFZzGSF1d2ncfO2+GYfUAY0j4Mvp+6fhqV9dwgCsDekBQRxyQpMSJHUFQjEJFGqNV6mZvyzj4ppbi2KpN5Ib5x81N7THudm+K/Pn+L7ffYyonL8RVvLJgrZ+zhgQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"interval\"\n        title=\"interval\"\n        src=\"/static/63f2320b2a130045306942cbf2545e13/f058b/observable_creation3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63f2320b2a130045306942cbf2545e13/c26ae/observable_creation3.png 158w,\n/static/63f2320b2a130045306942cbf2545e13/6bdcf/observable_creation3.png 315w,\n/static/63f2320b2a130045306942cbf2545e13/f058b/observable_creation3.png 630w,\n/static/63f2320b2a130045306942cbf2545e13/b2cef/observable_creation3.png 847w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h2>of</h2>\n<p>:전달된 값들을 생성해낸다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3f0c88b38a93268f60db622f2d6bf02a/e80ac/obs